							<p>Our story begins in a small
								Italian town called Montorio,
								in the little-known Region
								of Molise. Before there were
								pizzerias, people would
								get their bread and pizza
								from a bakery. My grandparents, Peppino and Ida,
								opened their bakery in the
								1940’s, using only the finest
								ingredients and producing the
								finest products in the region.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="col-md-6">
							<h5 class="text-pink">PIZZAIOLO IS BORN</h5>
