								Petrella was destined to
								be a Pizzaiolo, following in
								the footsteps of both his
								grand-parents and parents.
								Unable to find great quality,
								authentic pizza in Toronto,
								Luigi opened Pizzaiolo
								in November 2000. His
								mission, “I want people to
								know what a great pizza
								tastes like”.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="row">
