							<h5 class="text-pink">ARRIVING IN CANADA</h5>
							<p>After emigrating to Canada
								and settling in Toronto in
								the 1960’s, my parents, Tony
								and Anna, along with my
								uncle Gino, opened their first
								Italian restaurant. In 1967, La
								Gondola opened at Wilson
								& Bathurst, serving the most
								delicious pasta & pizza in
								the city</p>
						</div>
						<div class="col-md-6">
							<h5 class="text-pink">VALUES</h5>
