								because of our “Love of
								Food”, and to this day, we
								are incredibly proud of
								our heritage and the fact
								we have not changed the
								quality of our pizza. With
								Love, Passion, Family and a
								commitment to Quality, we
								are proud to have served
								you, your friends and
								families for over 20 years.
								</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="row">
